    <title>Revisiting the CEO Effect Through a Machine Learning Lens</title>
    <updated>2025-04-02T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Hajime Shimao, Sung Joo Kim, Warut Khern-Am-Nuai, Maxime C. Cohen</name>
